callouts.title: Pythagorean Theorem
callouts.content: In a right triangle, the square of the hypotenuse equals the sum of squares of the other two sides.

callouts.title: Goldbach Conjecture
callouts.content: Every even integer greater than 2 is the sum of two primes.
